#: ../../source/for_developers/changelog.rst:126
msgid ""
"Fixes #691 (issue that arose if the base data directory was cleared). When "
"base directory is cleared plugin will now reset the value to the default."
msgstr ""
"Исправления №691 (проблема, возникавшая при очистке каталога базовых "
